d in commercial spaces.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 30. Aug 2021) 0aCooking (Insects) 0aCooking (Insects). 0aEdible insects. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Agriculture & Food (see also POLITICAL SCIENCE / Public Policy / Agriculture & Food Policy).2bisacsh1 aAnnan, Kofi, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBeckhoven, Robèrt Van, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBlumenfeld-Schaap, Diane.1 aCalis, Margot, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDicke, Marcel, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aFabre, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aFresco, Louise O., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aGruijters, Katja, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKlunder, Harmke, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMartin, Daniella, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPeters, Marian, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRamos Anaya, Edoardo, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRedzepi, René, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aRuig, Jan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aTakken-Kaminker, Françoise.1 aVantomme, Paul, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aVerbon, Johan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWijffels, Herman, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aWind, Pierre, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 avan Gurp, Henk, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe Gruy